You said it.

151
00:08:16,980 --> 00:08:18,860
That's what I expect from Kotoko.

152
00:08:18,860 --> 00:08:22,200
Kin-chan. What do you mean "You said it", Kin-chan?

153
00:08:22,200 --> 00:08:25,280
You simply don't want Kotoko and Irie to get closer.

154
00:08:25,280 --> 00:08:27,850
Shut up!

155
00:08:27,900 --> 00:08:30,600
This is no time to joke around.

156
00:08:33,500 --> 00:08:35,290
His family has a big problem.

157
00:08:35,290 --> 00:08:36,910
It's Irie.

158
00:08:36,910 --> 00:08:39,170
I can see him pretending to be tough.

159
00:08:39,170 --> 00:08:40,670
But I'm sure he feels

160
00:08:40,670 --> 00:08:43,100
lonely and anxious.

161
00:08:43,100 --> 00:08:45,030
Kotoko, if there's something that you can do,

162
00:08:45,030 --> 00:08:47,050
