163
00:08:48,870 --> 00:08:51,350
You're right.

164
00:08:51,350 --> 00:08:53,360
If there's something I can do,

165
00:08:53,360 --> 00:08:55,740
I'll help you with it.

166
00:08:55,800 --> 00:08:59,200
So don't hesitate and just ask anytime.

167
00:08:59,200 --> 00:09:01,500
Thank you, Kin-chan.

168
00:09:05,620 --> 00:09:08,390
It's about time. I have to go.

169
00:09:08,390 --> 00:09:09,780
Goodbye.

170
00:09:09,780 --> 00:09:12,660
-See you.
-Bye bye.

171
00:09:15,240 --> 00:09:18,250
Hey, Kin-chan! What was that about?

172
00:09:18,250 --> 00:09:20,070
