176
00:09:26,700 --> 00:09:30,240
I'm not talking about something so low-leveled.

177
00:09:30,240 --> 00:09:32,040
It's like I'm sending

178
00:09:32,040 --> 00:09:35,730
support to my enemy.

179
00:09:35,730 --> 00:09:37,430
