180
00:09:37,430 --> 00:09:39,080
If I take advantage of this situation

181
00:09:39,100 --> 00:09:41,580
and take Kotoko from them,

182
00:09:41,580 --> 00:09:45,950
it'd make me less of a man.

183
00:09:45,950 --> 00:09:48,560
After all, you and Kotoko,

184
00:09:48,560 --> 00:09:52,890
are so similar.

185
00:09:52,900 --> 00:09:56,100
Because what you just said,

186
00:09:56,100 --> 00:09:58,910
