187
00:09:58,910 --> 00:10:03,040
'I don't care about myself, but I want the person I love to be happy'.

188
00:10:03,040 --> 00:10:05,520
That's true! You're like her!

189
00:10:05,600 --> 00:10:08,270
You and Kotoko are,

190
