It's too spicy. You shouldn't eat it.

208
00:11:06,710 --> 00:11:09,450
It's hot.

209
00:11:15,910 --> 00:11:17,690
Naoki,

210
00:11:17,690 --> 00:11:19,920
what was that sound?

211
